    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was maybe a five, six villages belong to that-- to that village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, and I was working very, very good, and more was I working, more it was better for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the business was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the boss, when I came the main-- main office, it was in Kolki.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now, and I came sometimes as they was laughing for me one time, a young boy, and I take a job like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most of them older people.",
